headline: FWIW at Least Someone Said It Out Loud
sentences:
{Direct Rumble Link}
House GOP representative Jim Jordan delivered a speech on the floor today that essentially encapsulates most of the current issues that have become the collective weight from the jackboot.
While the jackboot on our neck doesn’t seem to be getting any lighter, at least someone says what’s going on out loud.
Insofar as congressional speeches have value, this summary from Jordan is quite succinct.
